Rating: 4
This gets four forks because it is so simple and so delicious. I agree that the low end of the garlic amount called for is plenty-- mine with 4 was still very garlic-hot. This is just what I was hoping for! I did add a little bit of lemon (about 1/2 lemon) but it tasted good before I did that too.

Rating: 3
This was delicious and my guests eagerly asked for the leftovers (ended up making quite a bit because I used dried beans instead of canned and the bag made way more than what would ordinarily be found in two cans). I followed the advice of others and used only 4 cloves of garlic. This is a keeper.

