Rating: 4
If you don't like the power of fresh garlic, use the same number of garlic cloves and boil them first in water for a minute or two. This calms the flavor down a bit!

Rating: 3
We love this recipe. It's much like hummus, but easier to make (no need for tahini). Very nice with grilled pita bread.

Rating: 3
I wanted a quick and easy recipe to make. I had all of the ingredients on hand and it was a snap to make -- with little clean up. I would use less garlic next time (or smaller cloves) because it can really take over the flavor. Next time I will serve it with more interesting, flavored crackers. And if I were more adventurous, I would vary it with other ingredients.